            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Septimus <expan><abbr>vix</abbr><ex>it</ex></expan> <lb n="2"/>LX Am<supplied reason="lost">a</supplied>sia <expan><abbr>an</abbr><ex>norum</ex></expan> V <lb n="3"/>Viator <expan><abbr>an</abbr><ex>norum</ex></expan> X <lb n="4"/>Escitatus <lb n="5"/>viv<expan><ex>u</ex><abbr>s</abbr></expan> et Tertia <lb n="6"/>vivi posu<lb break="no" n="7"/>erunt Se&amp;lt;p&amp;gt;tumi<lb break="no" n="8"/>nus <expan><abbr>an</abbr><ex>norum</ex></expan> XV
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Oberhalb des Inschriftfeldes vier phalerae (oder paterae?); darüber ein Adler. Reste von roter Farbe in den Buchstaben. (B): Neumann; Farka u. a.; Hild: Leseabweichungen.</p>
            </div>
